  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aimed to describe and understand the decision making process in neonatology in
      situations of limiting of withdraw life sustaining treatments, by conducting interviews with
      physicians from one neonatology unit.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
