  <eligibility>
    <study_pop>
      <textblock>
        This study concerns the situation of new born for whom a decision making regarding limiting
        or withdrawing treatments is emerging, but only the physicians are involved as subjects of
        the study and seen in interviews.
      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Non-Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Physicians in charge of new born babies for whom a decision making regarding limiting
             or withdrawing treatments is emerging.

          -  physicians' informed consent to participate to an interview

          -  parents' informed consent to collect data concerning their new born.

        Exclusion Criteria:

        - Not fluent French speaker
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
